original_title: Jasperina de Jong: De Jasperina Show
overview: In her first show Jasperina de Jong sings songs about Sibylle, the last striptease dancer, about a Bach concert with a Woodstock vibe, about a nunnery where everyone gets addicted to mind-altering substances, about a provincial girl who travels to Amsterdam, and many more.
title: Jasperina de Jong: The Jasperina Show
